[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.0"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes affect Tails 1.0.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails
1.0.1|news/version_1.0.1]] as soon as possible.

Details
=======

 - Iceweasel and its bundled NSS: [[!mfsa 2014-48]], [[!mfsa 2014-52]],
   [[!mfsa 2014-49]]
 - dpkg: [[!debsa2014 2915]], [[!debsa2014 2953]]
 - libmms: [[!debsa2014 2916]]
 - linux: [[!debsa2014 2926]], [[!debsa2014 2949]]
 - gnutls: [[!debsa2014 2944]]
 - openssl: [[!debsa2014 2950]]
